  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether the addition of an animated skin surgery
      educational video to conventional in-person surgery consultation will help reduce
      pre-operative anxiety in patients awaiting outpatient skin surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This will be an randomized controlled pilot study. Subjects will be randomized to either
      receive an animated video along with conventional consultation OR receive a conventional
      consultation only. Pre-operative anxiety will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
